{"tid":1684801,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「主線任」112 拎唔到不反，手足我地開花好唔好？","createTime":"2019-10-31T09:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T09:48:14.000Z","uid":293226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9dd91ad4d93e9126f80c70badfdc06fa5d62fb1c","tid":1684801,"uid":293226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:25:55.000Z","msg":"⚠️⚠️⚠️突發⚠️⚠️⚠️<br />\n11月2號維園集會上訴失敗<br />\n<br />\n集會籌委會於10月30日晚收到警方通知，就維園集會發出禁止通知，集會籌委會即時提出上訴，經過公眾集會及遊行上訴委員裁決，集會上訴失敗。<br />\n<br />\n唔想打搞大家去lkf玩既心情，但係離112得返2日。去飲酒之前傾埋我地果日去邊先好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國殤日除咗班老鼠亂開槍謀殺手足之外，我地都做得唔錯呀。<br />\n<br />\n所以小弟建議，再次各區開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屯門<br />\n荃灣<br />\n沙田<br />\n深水埗<br />\n黃大仙<br />\n灣仔（和理非場？）<br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪大家要考試，所以感覺上少咗人，但我唔信大家會放棄，112係主線任，如果主線任都做唔好，我地點對得住班被捕手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fUUmbz9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfUUmbz9.jpg&h=2081d756&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP牌推唔到，直接開post。"},{"pid":"a9286494133e1bc5ba6b60100e75b41cee414a48","tid":1684801,"uid":293226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:27:24.000Z","msg":"有意見就講出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔想到112果日先起身睇我要去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b5b22e27da13982d8c8ae41103fd9875cd3213","tid":1684801,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:27:29.000Z","msg":"